(##Workflow for Transferring Listings Between Platforms) Tj
T*
(1. Open the source marketplace listing.) Tj
T*
(2. Copy product title, price, condition, and description.) Tj
T*
(3. Download or collect listing images.) Tj
T*
(4. Open the destination website CMS product form.) Tj
T*
(5. Paste product details into the correct fields.) Tj
T*
(6. Assign product category and relevant tags.) Tj
T*
(7. Upload and arrange images in display order.) Tj
T*
(8. Add SKU, inventory details, and listing status.) Tj
T*
(9. Publish or save as draft based on client preference.) Tj
T*
(10. Perform a final quality check for completeness and formatting.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(This workflow ensures repeatable quality, faster turnaround, and consistent listing standards) Tj
T*
(across platforms.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(---) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
